public class PageFactoryClass

using custom page factory solution to get locators from external file with PageObjectModel advantage of page factory: 1- Whenever we use a WebElement, it will go and find it again so you shouldnâ€™t see StaleElementExceptions 2- On PageFactory Initialization, the proxies are configured, but the WebElements are not found that point. So we wonâ€™t get NoSuchElementException. 3- robust script
